      "bookSlug": "galatians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Galatians 5:23",
      "text": "ܡܟܝܟܘܬܐ ܡܤܝܒܪܢܘܬܐ ܥܠ ܗܠܝܢ ܢܡܘܤܐ ܠܐ ܤܝܡ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
