      "bookSlug": "galatians",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Galatians 5:25",
      "text": "ܢܚܐ ܗܟܝܠ ܒܪܘܚܐ ܘܠܪܘܚܐ ܢܫܠܡ ܀",
